Playwright Automation (High Level)

I use Playwright for end-to-end automation testing.

I automate critical user flows, not everything blindly.

Common scenarios I cover:

Login and authentication

Form submissions

Navigation and role-based access

I follow Page Object Model, so test cases are reusable and easy to maintain.

Why Playwright

Fast and reliable

Works well across browsers

Good for CI/CD integration

Development + Testing Mindset

Having both development and automation experience helps me:

